House on Haunted Hill
.
A perrenial favorite of the "Shock Theatre" TV circuit, House on Haunted Hill stars Vincent Price as a sinister gent who owns a sinister mansion on a sinister hill. He offers several of his enemies $10,000 each - if they agree to spend the night in the crumbling old mansion. Price festively gives each of his guests a tiny coffin containing a handgun, then he proceeds to set in motion any number of gadgets and devices designed to frighten the guests into using their weapons. (Black and White)
